# Mars Lander Simulation

## Overview
A smart landing system that simulates spacecraft descent using sensors and controlled actuation. :contentReference[oaicite:10]{index=10}

---

## Features
- Environmental sensing (Temp, Pressure, UV)
- Data transmission via Wi-Fi
- Controlled landing simulation

